name: NYDailyNews
text:
RT @snydenydn: The U.S. government is auctioning off 126 Fyre Fest-related items that were seized by the feds from the disgraced organizer Billy McFarland. 

Proceeds from the sale of the items will go toward victims who were duped into attending the disastrous event.
